edu.uidaho.junicon.grammars.common

Interface IParserCache

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    ParserCache

    public interface IParserCache
    Provides literal and parse-tree caches for parsed statements.
    Provides a map from string keys to parsed literals for later use by the interpreter.
    Provides a map from statements to parse trees for use in the interpreter transform to hold parsed function templates.
